com.poesys.accounting.dataloader.newaccounting

Class Reimburse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.poesys.accounting.dataloader.newaccounting.Reimburse

  • public class Reimburse
extends java.lang.Object
    A data transfer object that represents the association of a reimbursing transaction item to a receivable transaction item; contains some combination of reimbursed amount and allocated amount (an amount not included in the reimbursing item to be applied to the receivable--a writeoff, in other words); see Item for details on constraints
    Author:
    Robert J. Muller
